s/global-variable-styles.css","site-lib/styles/main-styles.css","site-lib/rss.xml"],"allFiles":["hot_lizard-music_video-process.html","pasted-image-20260705171423.png","pasted-image-20260705171423.html","pasted-image-20260705171134.png","pasted-image-20260705171134.html","pasted-image-20260705171056.png","pasted-image-20260705171056.html","pasted-image-20260705170943.png","pasted-image-20260705170943.html","pasted-image-20260705165216.png","pasted-image-20260705165216.html","pasted-image-20260705165014.png","pasted-image-20260705165014.html","pasted-image-20260704150018.png","pasted-image-20260704150018.html","pasted-image-20260704132512.png","pasted-image-20260704132512.html","pasted-image-20260621154331.png","pasted-image-20260621154331.html","pasted-image-20260621154205.png","pasted-image-20260621154205.html","pasted-image-20260621153043.png","pasted-image-20260621153043.html","pasted-image-20260621153028.png","pasted-image-20260621153028.html","site-lib/scripts/graph-wasm.wasm","site-lib/fonts/70cc7ff27245e82ad414.ttf","site-lib/fonts/454577c22304619db035.ttf","site-lib/fonts/52ac8f3034507f1d9e53.ttf","site-lib/fonts/05b618077343fbbd92b7.ttf","site-lib/fonts/4bb6ac751d1c5478ff3a.woff2","site-lib/fonts/c504db5c06caaf7cdfba.woff2","site-lib/fonts/01dcbad1bac635f9c9cd.woff2","site-lib/media/6155340132a851f6089e.svg","site-lib/media/2308ab1944a6bfa5c5b8.svg","site-lib/html/file-tree-content.html","site-lib/scripts/webpage.js","site-lib/scripts/graph-wasm.js","site-lib/scripts/graph-render-worker.js","site-lib/media/favicon.png","site-lib/styles/obsidian.css","site-lib/styles/theme.css","site-lib/styles/global-variable-styles.css","site-lib/styles/main-styles.css"],"webpages":{"hot_lizard-music_video-process.html":{"title":"Hot_Lizard Music_Video Process","icon":"","description":"This page is a full documentation on the process of how this fanmade project came to exist.Concept/Made up Reference for the Brain Scene<img alt=\"Pasted image 20260621154205.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260621154205.png\" target=\"_self\">Another reference image in use<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260705171423.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260705171423.png\" target=\"_self\">Remove/add more realism than there was before.It is composed of multiple components. Starting with the principled BSDF for most realism and detail and slowly stripped of everything unnecessary through the adage of extra nodes and shader layers, for stylization purposes. Inspiration came from this videoThe point currently is to have a stylized blobby wet brain that has the style of can be deduced to be made by or have a relation to AI technologys.What this specifically is, is the sludge that the brain turns into (can be referenced towards and interpreted in the song).\nBecause the end result of AI Image and video generation is a design that devolves into, functions as and or somewhat looks like sludge. In other words \"Slop\".Its a combination of everything, turning it into a vicious liquid metaphorically.\nAdded Subsurface Scattering for extra Realism.\nShader Node Setup rendered result:Without Subsurface Scattering<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260621153028.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260621153028.png\" target=\"_self\">With Subsurface Scattering<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260621153043.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260621153043.png\" target=\"_self\">A result looking more like the initial concept:<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260621154331.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260621154331.png\" target=\"_self\">Shader Node setup currently in use<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260705170943.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260705170943.png\" target=\"_self\">Beginning of modeling out the main scene the music video will take place in<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260704132512.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260704132512.png\" target=\"_self\">Searching on House listing sites for apartment and what low income apartments look like was a great reference point to start getting the look right in future development.Downloaded a Potentially placeholder computer model from sketchfab and modified it. <br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260705165216.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260705165216.png\" target=\"_self\"><br>Info\n\"Personal Computer\" (<a rel=\"noopener nofollow\" class=\"external-link is-unresolved\" href=\"https://skfb.ly/6YEDU\" target=\"_self\">https://skfb.ly/6YEDU</a>) by Juan Foo is licensed under Creative Commons Attribution (<a rel=\"noopener nofollow\" class=\"external-link is-unresolved\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\" target=\"_self\">http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</a>). <img alt=\"Pasted image 20260705171134.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260705171134.png\" target=\"_self\"> Modeled out the first window.\n<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260704150018.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260704150018.png\" target=\"_self\">Two Bevels were used. One bevel for the hinge and another one to add a little more detail and curvature to the inner frame.Current state of the Scene<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260705165014.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260705165014.png\" target=\"_self\">","aliases":[],"inlineTags":[],"frontmatterTags":[],"headers":[{"heading":"Jun 21 2026","level":1,"id":"Jun_21_2026_0"},{"heading":"Stylized shading method","level":2,"id":"Stylized_shading_method_0"},{"heading":"July 03 2026","level":1,"id":"July_03_2026_0"},{"heading":"July 04 2026","level":1,"id":"July_04_2026_0"},{"heading":"July 05 2026","level":1,"id":"July_05_2026_0"}],"links":[],"author":"","coverImageURL":".","fullURL":"hot_lizard-music_video-process.html","pathToRoot":".","attachments":["pasted-image-20260621154205.html","pasted-image-20260705171423.html","pasted-image-20260621153028.html","pasted-image-20260621153043.html","pasted-image-20260621154331.html","pasted-image-20260705170943.html","pasted-image-20260704132512.html","pasted-image-20260705165216.html","pasted-image-20260705171134.html","pasted-image-20260704150018.html","pasted-image-20260705165014.html"],"createdTi